  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate the safety and tolerability of single ascending (SAD)
      and multiple (MD) oral dose of GLPG0555 compared to placebo.

      Also, pharmacokinetics (PK) and pharmacodynamics (PD) of GLPG555 after single and multiple
      oral administration will be evaluated, and, if applicable, the maximum tolerated dose
      determined.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
